content.rendered:
Directed by Thirumala Kishore.

Written by K.N. Vijay Kumar.

Cast Ram Pothineni(Hari (as Ram)). Keerthy Suresh(Sailaja). Sathyaraj(Srinivas). V.K. Naresh(Hari’s father (as Naresh)). Vamsi Krishna(Babji). Rohini(Sailaja’s mother). Pradeep Singh Rawat(Maharshi). Pragathi(Hari’s mother). Joy Badlani(Radhiya). Vijayakumar(Sailaja’s grandfather (as Vijay Kumar)). Sreemukhi(Swecha). Krishna Bhagavan(Srinivasa’s friend). Prince Cecil(Ashok).Shani Salmon. Chaitanya Krishna(Vijaya Krishna)

Language Telugu.

Producer Ravi Kishore.

Production Sri Sravanthi Films. Sri Sravanthi Movies. Goldmines Telefilms.
